opennlp.ccg.alignment
Enum Status

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<Status>
      opennlp.ccg.alignment.Status
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Status>
public enum Status
extends Enum<Status>

A set of Enum constants for describing the status of a mapping, either as POSSIBLE or SURE.

Statuses have a corresponding abbreviated form for use when mappings are formatted and parsed as strings. The enum constants are arranged in order of strength of surety, so that Enum.ordinal() returns numbers in order of increasing surety.

Author:
Scott Martin
See Also:
MappingFormat
